\doTocEntry\toclof{}{\csname a:TocLink\endcsname{1}{x1-78006}{}{\numberline {15.7}{\ignorespaces $\bar {R}$ and $\kappa $ are two concentration parameters for circular data. $\bar {R}$ is easier to calculate than $\kappa $ (using Equation~\ref {eq:circularR}), and can be converted to $\kappa $ in order to fit a von Mises distribution to the data.\medskip \relax }}}{223}\relax 
